// * `ax`: accelerometer X axis (normalized, typically [-1, 1])
// * `ay`: accelerometer Y axis (normalized, typically [-1, 1])
// * `az`: accelerometer Z axis (normalized, typically [-1, 1])
//   - Output magnitude is clamped to [0, 1].
